<link href="adcp.css" rel="stylesheet"><entry><xh5> as far as • so far as</xh5><p> <i>as far as—</i>1. up to a point or place mentioned: We went <u>as far as</u> the Marble Lodge, a keeper’s cottage, and came back the same way. 2. to the extent that: <u>As far as</u> I can tell, people reply according to what their experience and knowledge is and to the best of their ability.</p><p> <i>so far as</i>— = as far as 2: <u>So far as</u> I can remember, I’ve always been success-driven and goal-oriented, and all it’s gotten me is a mediocre job.</p> </entry>
